Bash(quinn-code-writer "Feature: Implementation of UserCards adapter layer for managing user card collections in Cosmos DB. This adapter will handle write operations (Scribe) for adding cards to a user''s collection, following the established CQRS pattern with Commands folder structure. UserCards Cosmos schema: {partition: userId, id: cardId, cardId: card.Id, userId: user.Id, setId: card.set.Id, collected: [{finish: {nonfoil|foil|etched}, special: {none|altered|signed|proof}, count: {count}}]}

User Story: Create the Cosmos DB document model for UserCards data storage, including the main item class and nested collection structure. UserCardItem class defined in Cosmos adapter project, follows established Item patterns, properties match schema requirements. Inherits from CosmosItem base class, JsonProperty attributes for property naming, CollectedItem nested class for collection data, proper partition key and ID override.

Task: Create UserCardItem Class at src/Lib.Adapter.Scryfall.Cosmos/Apis/CosmosItems/UserCardItem.cs. Reference src/Lib.Adapter.Scryfall.Cosmos/Apis/CosmosItems/UserInfoItem.cs. Inherits from CosmosItem base class, override Id and Partition properties, use JsonProperty attributes, init setters. Properties: UserId (json_property user_id), CardId (json_property card_id), SetId (json_property set_id), CollectedList (json_property collected, type: List<CollectedItem>). Id property returns CardId value, Partition property returns UserId value.")
